entries.title_d: Hunt down a Hutt Transport and destroy their spice cargo
entries.title: Dantooine System: Destroy the Spice Transport
entries.quest_target_d: A high speed multi purpose transport
entries.quest_location_d: A smuggler lane in the Dantooine System
entries.quest_escort_d: This is an importan shipment, expect heavy resistance.
entries.failed_escape: \#pcontrast3 CorSec: < \#pcontrast1 The transport has made the jump, now it is up to the local police forces of their target world to defend from the spice menace. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 An escorting craft has been destroyed, %DI remain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Escort craft are considered a priority target. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assassinate_success: \#pcontrast3 CorSec: < \#pcontrast1 Great job, that is one spice shipment that won't be making its way to its destination. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 CorSec: < \#pcontrast1 You will need to move quick, they are closer to their second jump point than we anticipated. Uploading their transponder signal to your nav computer now. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 CorSec: < \#pcontrast1 You are not far ahead of the transport, we will notify you in a moment of their arrival. \#pcontrast3 >
